---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import FadeUp from '../../components/animations/FadeUp.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Zenith Banking Case Study - Fintech UX/UI Design" 
  description="How Innovate transformed Zenith Banking's digital experience, resulting in a 200% increase in user engagement and 2M+ active users."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@graph": [
        {
          "@type": "Article",
          "@id": "https://innovate-proto.vercel.app/work/zenith-banking#article",
          "headline": "Zenith Banking: Reimagining the Future of Personal Finance",
          "description": "A comprehensive case study on the digital transformation of Zenith Banking.",
          "image": "https://innovate-proto.vercel.app/projects/zenith-hero.jpg",
          "author": { "@id": "https://innovate-proto.vercel.app/#organization" },
          "publisher": { "@id": "https://innovate-proto.vercel.app/#organization" },
          "datePublished": "2024-03-15",
          "mainEntityOfPage": { "@id": "https://innovate-proto.vercel.app/work/zenith-banking#webpage" }
        },
        {
          "@type": "WebPage",
          "@id": "https://innovate-proto.vercel.app/work/zenith-banking#webpage",
          "url": "https://innovate-proto.vercel.app/work/zenith-banking",
          "name": "Zenith Banking Case Study",
          "breadcrumb": { "@id": "https://innovate-proto.vercel.app/work/zenith-banking#breadcrumb" }
        },
        {
          "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
          "@id": "https://innovate-proto.vercel.app/work/zenith-banking#breadcrumb",
          "itemListElement": [
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://innovate-proto.vercel.app/" },
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Work", "item": "https://innovate-proto.vercel.app/work" },
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Zenith Banking", "item": "https://innovate-proto.vercel.app/work/zenith-banking" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
    </script>
  </Fragment>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-24">
    <FadeUp nojs={true}>
      <span class="text-neutral-500 font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sm mb-6 block">Case Study / 2024</span>
      <h1 class="text-[clamp(3.5rem,10vw,12rem)] font-black tracking-[-0.05em] mb-12 uppercase leading-[0.8]">ZENITH <br /> BANKING.</h1>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 border-y border-neutral-100 py-12">
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 mb-4">Client</h4>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold">Zenith Financial Group</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 mb-4">Services</h4>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold">Product Design, UX/UI, Mobile App</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 mb-4">Results</h4>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-black">2M+ Users / 4.9 App Rating</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </FadeUp>
  </section>

  <section class="px-6 md:px-24 mb-32">
    <div class="aspect-[21/9] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[3rem] bg-neutral-100 shadow-2xl" data-reveal="image">
      <img src="/projects/zenith-hero.jpg" alt="Zenith Banking Hero" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <FadeUp>
      <div class="prose prose-xl prose-neutral max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-10 tracking-tight">The Challenge.</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
          Zenith Banking, a legacy financial institution, faced a critical challenge: their digital infrastructure was failing to meet the expectations of a new generation of mobile-first users. With an outdated interface and complex navigation, user retention was dropping, and the brand was losing ground to agile fintech startups.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
          The primary goal was to completely rethink the mobile banking experience—moving away from traditional transactional models towards a holistic financial management tool that felt personal, intuitive, and secure.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-10 tracking-tight mt-32">Our Approach.</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
          We began with a month-long research phase, conducting deep-dive interviews with over 100 Zenith customers. We discovered that the main friction point wasn't just functionality, but the *emotional* weight of financial management. Users felt anxious, not empowered.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-20">
          <div class="bg-[#fafafa] p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-neutral-100">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Glassmorphic UI</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-500">We implemented a sleek, modern aesthetic using glassmorphism to create a sense of depth and transparency—literally and figuratively reflecting the brand's new values.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#fafafa] p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-neutral-100">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Predictive UX</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-500">Using machine learning patterns, we designed a dashboard that predicts user needs, surfacing relevant actions like bill payments or saving goals before the user has to search for them.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-10 tracking-tight mt-32">The Results.</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
          The launch of the new Zenith Banking app was a resounding success. Within the first six months, the platform saw a 200% increase in daily active users and a 45% improvement in customer satisfaction scores (NPS).
        </p>

        <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-black pl-8 my-20">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight italic">"Innovate didn't just redesign our app; they redefined our relationship with our customers. The results speak for themselves."</p>
          <cite class="text-neutral-500 font-bold block mt-4">— Elena S., CEO at Zenith Financial</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </FadeUp>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-40 bg-black text-white text-center">
    <FadeUp>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-12 tracking-tight">READY TO TRANSFORM?</h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-12 py-6 bg-white text-black rounded-full font-bold text-xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform">Start a Project</a>
    </FadeUp>
  </section>
</Layout>
